{
  "stem": "19352.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 45.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Teacher.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she has the-- she said to us that you are sitting there like the Jews in a mikveh.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said-- I stood up and I said, I don't belong here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was not allowed to do it because this was a special place, that you have to stay there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I can't do what you want to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went again to the director and told him the story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is politic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was not allowed to belong to organization, even, when you went to high school because school is not a political ground to-- especially to children, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not going back to there, even you're going to dismiss me from the school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, don't worry about-- we're going to talk about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Would you explain for us what she meant when she said that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was-- you have a-- a very heavy rifle in you hands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't hold it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then everyone was lying like, you know, really very bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She can said it in another way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Come-- I know it's very heavy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come stood up, and I show you how to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The meaning of the word--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mikveh is a-- a ritual bath.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a Orthodox shul, they have a-- a-- a-- like a swimming-- a swimming pool, but in a smaller thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everyone, woman and man, when he had to have intercourse, he had to go to the mikveh, to this thing, and-- and take a bath.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she also take a bath-- not together, but separate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Man is separate woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- she's trying to say that we cannot fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
